data.description: Back on the market and ready for new home owner!  Don't miss a chance to turn this Ewa Gentry home into a true masterpiece. Bring your creativity, paint swatches, and your vision, and schedule a showing today to unlock the potential that awaits within these walls. This is your opportunity to make this house a home once more! Two-story, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom with an open loft area on the second floor, perfect for a home office, playroom, or additional living space. One bedroom and one bathroom on the first floor, offering flexibility and accessibility. Covered carport and a driveway with a low maintenance yard. Nearby parks, schools, and shopping centers provide convenience for daily living. Plus, Ewa Beach's beautiful beaches are just a short drive away, offering endless opportunities for relaxation and recreation. Some photos have been enhanced.
